&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cottonwood Residential is hiring! We are looking for an Assistant Property Manager to join our team at Cottonwood Ridgeview Apartments in Plano, TX. Apply today!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
