&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Competitive base pay and quarterly bonus structure!&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Full health, vision, dental, life, and disability benefits - available within 1-30 days!&lt;/li&gt;
