&lt;li&gt;Exceptional multi-tasking and communication skills, both oral and written.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Good understanding of basic accounting practices.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Entrata Core experience is a plus.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of Fair Housing Laws is preferred.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Weekend availability is required.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Summary of an&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Assistant Property Manager&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
